title: Videohive - After Effects Project Files - Stain of Dishonor
description:
- CS4 , CS5 compatible
- Full HD resolution 1080p
- 8 videoholders
- 13 textholders
- 8 additional textholders
- Fully customization (texture, color)
- No additional plugin needed 
There are two projects created, full and prerender one. Full version is with all effects (Trapcode Particular, VideoCopilot Optical Flares) used for this animation.
Prerendered project is all prerender project so you DONT NEED ANY ADDITIONAL PLUGINS. 

Project contain 2 project name place holders ( at the begining and at the end of the project), company info, 8 video holders, 10 text holders and 8 additional video text holders.
